# pipenv
#   According to pypa/pipenv#598, it is recommended to include Pipfile.lock in version control.
#   However, in case of collaboration, if used, it could be ignored.
#Pipfile.lock

# poetry
#   Similar to Pipfile.lock, poetry.lock is database-managed and should be checked in.
